{"tid":955949,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麻省理工學院成功研發物件縮小新技術！","createTime":"2018-12-25T23:55:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T10:16:32.000Z","uid":22675,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"9d9ae21f139fb57a8a250687483061533dc754b0","tid":955949,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T23:55:19.000Z","msg":"Follow Us     &times;<br />\n搜尋<br />\n<br />\n麻省理工學院成功研發物件縮小新技術！是多啦 A 夢縮小電筒嗎？<br />\n | Kay | 24-12-2018 12:44 |   | <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n有一集日本動畫《多啦 A 夢》是這樣的，大雄回到家中想跟多啦 A 夢借道具使用，幫忙翌日測驗順利，但發現多啦 A 夢竟然生了病，於是大雄決定用縮小電筒將自己變小，進入多啦 A 夢體內將系統重啟，以將受損組織修復。在現實中，將一件實物縮小看似是天方夜譚，但在美國 MIT 麻省理工學院的技術團隊眼中則不然，因為團隊透過對腦造影技術的逆向工程，研發一種能將物件縮小的新技術，甚至可將物件縮小至原本的 1/1000 尺寸。<br />\n<br />\n【相關新聞】Kia．麻省理工學院合作研發「讀心」智能車廂！AI 提升乘搭體驗<br />\n<br />\n【相關新聞】中國科學家研發新式可重寫紙張！DIY 手機殼另類選擇？<br />\n<br />\nMIT 麻省理工學院的技術團隊，以聚丙烯酸酯（Polyacrylate）物料來製作新結構，再將之浸泡在含有螢光素分子（fluorescein molecules）的溶液中。螢光素分子溶液被光線照射時，該分子就會依附在聚丙烯酸酯新結構上，之後藉雷射方法，將任何粒子放置在指定地方，再使用有阻隔聚丙烯酸酯負電作用的酸性物質，就可做到縮小新結構的效果。<br />\n<br />\n技術團隊認為該物件可以縮小了多少，就是取決於原本物件的大小，現時如 1 立方毫米的物體，約可達至 50 納米的精細度，而 1 立方厘米的物體，就只可達至最多 500 納米的精細度。大家關心的是，之後該技術會可以怎樣發展呢？技術團隊表示對應用於顯微鏡、手機光學元件等方面的組件，或許有所作為。但當然，何時能將之投入商業世界，就是言之尚早的事情了。"},{"pid":"518c0b973bf8b0312d806fdcf68659735dcaad8f","tid":955949,"uid":55533,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T23:57:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_p.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_y.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/1/1a/AntManYellowjacket.jpg/220px-AntManYellowjacket.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fthumb%2F1%2F1a%2FAntManYellowjacket.jpg%2F220px-AntManYellowjacket.jpg&h=8be7be71&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ace6e59dbd76cdda8983769e214d08a119403d92","tid":955949,"uid":91618,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T00:06:08.000Z","msg":"留名睇有人想縮細佢條嘢"},{"pid":"d17c708f4f5c132cc87fd759340e33df04ce3c4c","tid":955949,"uid":68220,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T00:11:29.000Z","msg":"縮小我男朋友個屎眼<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83033825a056a10b5df8d9d20f3de6a58ad0b197","tid":955949,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T01:23:43.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"e4aabf92f69855809ee31283ef2b55a4c3bbdc30","tid":955949,"uid":116455,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T01:25:16.000Z","msg":"幾時有放大功能，放大條撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34cb21066869ee86f9cebd75bf8a34c9fb79e8dc","tid":955949,"uid":389,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T02:54:57.000Z","msg":"EUV光刻變廢物"},{"pid":"d692967f328b7b009aaec23906e8c51bd0e19521","tid":955949,"uid":54733,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T03:01:26.000Z","msg":"縮細香港人就可以解決居住問題"},{"pid":"f3e948c206c351d21d1f0ab30de7d205b7f7ad2b","tid":955949,"uid":54524,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"d692967f328b7b009aaec23906e8c51bd0e19521","tid":955949,"uid":54733,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T03:01:26.000Z","msg":"縮細香港人就可以解決居住問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T03:05:51.000Z","msg":"係都縮細d大陸人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0582372f5a798b28b144f6767bec7238c6d15151","tid":955949,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T08:38:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\